curam.util.ctm.bom.uitab.impl

Class ApplicationConfigDependentBOMImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.ctm.bom.BusinessObjectModuleImpl
      • curam.util.ctm.bom.uitab.impl.ApplicationConfigDependentBOMImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BusinessObjectModule, DependentBOM

    public class ApplicationConfigDependentBOMImpl
extends BusinessObjectModuleImpl
implements DependentBOM
    This is the Dependent Business Object Module implementation for an Application Configuration BOM. An Application Configuration BOM consists of the .app file and its associated .properties file. Both are stored on the database in the AppResource table. This class is responsible for returning the list of dependencies for an Application BOM.
